list.name: Cat_Dog_kaggle_data.zip
list.detail:
Dataset by kaggle containing images to train a model to classify Dog and Cats Images 
 7100 images of dogs and cats by kaggle for training purpose Cat_Dog_data/Cat_Dog_data/train 
 1250 images of dogs and cats each by kaggle for testing purpose  Cat_Dog_data/Cat_Dog_data/test
